  "pages": [
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Although the discussion of\nequal suffrage in The Press has\nformally closed, so many\nwomen, prominent suffragets\nand anit-suffragets, have asked\nthat the ballot be continued,\nthat The Press has decided to\nrun it the remainder of this\nweek, In order that all who\nhave not voted may have the\nopportunity. Also, If they want\nto discuss the question some\nmore, the columns of this news\npaper always are open to them.\n\n\nThe Tacoma Times has Just\nended a similar discussion, and\nhundreds of women have ex-\npressed their Wills at the news\npaper poll. Equal suffrage won\nby a very large majority."
    }
  ]
